public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int n = 5;

        for (int i = n; i >= 1; i--) {  // Start from `n` and decrease to `1`
            for (int j = 1; j <= i; j++) {  // Print `*` up to `i`
                System.out.print("* ");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
Right-Inverted Triangle:
* * * * * 
* * * * 
* * * 
* * 
* 
